query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Danish','Greenlandic','None','Ukrainian','Irish Gaelic','Italian','Czech','Albanian','Finnish','Tatar') AND n.gender in ('f') AND n.name not like '%u%' AND it2.info in ('essays','tech info','LD quality of source','where now','salary history','LD master format','bottom 10 rank','birth date') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete+verified','cast','complete') AND it1.info not in ('where now','mpaa','printed media reviews','rating','LD video standard','LD laserdisc title','LD number of chapter stops','alternate versions') AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' AND cct1.kind in ('complete','cast') AND (t.title like '%sword%' OR t.title like '%man%' OR t.title like '%adventure%') AND k.keyword not like '%betray%' AND k.keyword not like '%vengeance%' AND k.keyword not like '%space%'
